Class AsyncTaskResult<TResult>

  • java.lang.Object
    • to.sven.androidrccar.common.utils.AsyncTaskResult<TResult>
  • Type Parameters:
    TResult - The type of the normal result

    public class AsyncTaskResult<TResult>
extends java.lang.Object
    This data class can be used as a result of AsyncTask. It provides an normal result oder an exception as result of the task.
